{
  "stem": "18470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 316.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- he left Holland, made it to America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the only-- well, he and another member of the family met us at the dockside when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by then I was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last couple of days, I think, were OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember being on deck very early in the morning, very early in the morning, as the ship pulled into-- Ober-- to, funny Oberwesel-- the ship pulled into the harbor in New York.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I caught glimpse of my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- that was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was terribly exciting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was down on the-- on the key.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the dock, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in the-- in like a DP camp, a detention camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Dutch had these holding centers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To their credit, they refused to send him back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the Germans had demanded his return, and they didn't return anybody, until they themselves were invaded.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So he was-- he was at this-- I guess, the equivalent of a DP camp throughout that period of time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think about eight months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- you know, it was end of the Depression.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only work that was available to the greenhorns, which is the immigrants were called, was in sweatshops.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he had a job in a recycling factory, clothing recycling factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember he earned a huge salary of $14 a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when my mother began working, it was $7 a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember our first apartment, rented for $28 a month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was on-- the first apartment we lived on 30th Street and Fourth Avenue-- and the second apartment we lived on the-- 29th street and Fourth Avenue.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
